Blob Storage Access Tiers (Highest to Lowest Storage Cost):

| Tier    | Storage Cost | Access Cost | Usage                    |
| ------- | ------------ | ----------- | ------------------------ |
| Hot     | Highest      | Lowest      | Frequently accessed data |
| Cool    | Medium       | Medium      | Infrequent access        |
| Cold    | Lower        | Higher      | Rare access              |
| Archive | Lowest       | Highest     | Long-term storage        |

# Real-Life Example:
For example, a company stores active data in Hot tier and archives old data.

# Real-Life Use Case:
A real-life use case is tiered data lifecycle management.

This table helps in selecting the right tier.
